title: (x) Please identify this beauty - Custom Logo {Günni}
content:
Hey everyone,

please help me identify [this beauty here](http://web.archive.org/web/20080909074306/http:/www.arcor.de/iimages/49/art_440x330_WFeIZquqZYvAqlaDimGq8meCkdOK.jpg)

Actually, I’m not talking about Mrs Ferrero-Waldner nor Monsieur Kouchner but about the [logo in the back](http://web.archive.org/web/20080909074306/http:/ue2008.fr/jsp/jahia/templates/PFUE/PFUE/i/bandeau_logo.png).

Thanks in advance and a nice sunny weekend!

Günni
